<% title "About" %>
<div class="grid_12">
<p>
The Civic OpenMedia system enables government agencies to publish public data sets over the Internet in machine-readable form. System tools help you define, collect, filter and organize information content prior to publishing. Web services provide access to published updates at scheduled intervals and through RESTful query interface. Using community sharing capabilities, you may access and exchange data standards, content and additional resources with other organizations. 
</p>
